FUNCTIONS UPDATES
=================
   - Databases included as argument of the functions (the user can decide to use different versions)
   - Bug fix in function match_SNV_GDKD(): "refined grep when matching missense mutations with specific variant specified in the database"
   - Bug fix in function match_CNV_CIVIC(): "avoid grepping exon deletion, deletion polymorphism.."
   - Bug fix in function get_levels_CIVIC(): "Evidence.Level" to "evidence_level" (changed in newer versions of CIViC)
   - Bug fix in function clean_levels(): "to avoid error if input is empty"
   - Bug fix "to aggregate duplicated evidences"

